        "id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_chem-203343.pdf_121_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Coefficients for the tentative empirical formula are derived by dividing each molar amount by the lesser of the two:",
        "bbox": [
