      {
        "id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_chem-203343.pdf_121_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Since the resulting ratio is one carbon to two oxygen atoms, the empirical formula is COz.",
